high_descs: Walk along the right side of the table and continue straight until you're facing the counter on the right side of the sink.
Pick up the mug on the counter.
Turn right and face the fridge.
Place the mug in the fridge to the left of the lettuce. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Place the mug in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, hang a left at the wall, turn left just before the fridge and turn right to walk to the counter ahead.
Pick up the white mug to the left of the microwave on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the black fridge on the left.
Put the mug inside the fridge on the lowest shelf to the left of the head of lettuce, chill it for seven seconds, remove it and close the door.
Turn around, hang a right towards the counter with the sink and turn right to face the microwave.
Put the chilled mug inside the microwave on a plate and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall, the turn left and walk across the room to the microwave.
Pick up the mug off of the counter to the left of the microwave.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left to face the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge and let it get cool for a couple seconds, then open the fridge and take out the mug and close the door.
Walk over to where the microwave is on the counter.
Open the microwave and put the cool mug inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cool mug in the microwave.
